{
  "__file": "wp_block",
  "title": "Image ronde avec texte qui supperpose",
  "content": "<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|liquid-large\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|liquid-large\"},\"margin\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|liquid-x-large\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|liquid-x-large\"}},\"dimensions\":{\"minHeight\":\"100%\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"min-height:100%;margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--liquid-x-large);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--liquid-x-large);padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--liquid-large);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--liquid-large)\"><!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"className\":\"relative\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|liquid-medium\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center relative\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"30%\",\"className\":\"absolute\",\"style\":{\"border\":{\"radius\":{\"topLeft\":\"100px\",\"topRight\":\"100px\",\"bottomLeft\":\"100px\",\"bottomRight\":\"100px\"}},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"right\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"600px\",\"justifyContent\":\"left\",\"wideSize\":\"100%\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center absolute\" style=\"border-top-left-radius:100px;border-top-right-radius:100px;border-bottom-left-radius:100px;border-bottom-right-radius:100px;padding-right:0;padding-left:0;flex-basis:30%\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"left\":\"0\"},\"blockGap\":\"0\",\"margin\":{\"top\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\"}},\"dimensions\":{\"minHeight\":\"100%\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"justifyContent\":\"left\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"min-height:100%;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-left:0\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":254,\"aspectRatio\":\"1\",\"scale\":\"cover\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"align\":\"center\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\",\"style\":{\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fit\",\"flexSize\":null},\"color\":{\"duotone\":[\"#4A4A4A\",\"#85AD94\"]}}} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"http://naturapets.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/qui-sommes-nous-01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-254\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1;object-fit:cover\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"100%\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"right\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\",\"contentSize\":\"50%\",\"justifyContent\":\"right\",\"wideSize\":\"100%\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"padding-right:0;padding-left:0;flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|liquid-large\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"wrap\",\"justifyContent\":\"right\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"stretch\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:heading {\"style\":{\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"var:preset|color|secondary\"}}},\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"300\",\"lineHeight\":\"1\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|small\"}},\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fill\",\"flexSize\":null}},\"textColor\":\"secondary\",\"fontSize\":\"x-large\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-secondary-color has-text-color has-link-color has-x-large-font-size\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--small);font-style:normal;font-weight:300;line-height:1\">Une humaine motivée, un poilu déterminé, une idée devenue réalitée.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"7px\",\"padding\":{\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|liquid-large\"}},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"var:preset|color|secondary\"}}},\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.2\"},\"layout\":{\"selfStretch\":\"fill\",\"flexSize\":null}},\"textColor\":\"secondary\",\"fontSize\":\"liquid-small\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-secondary-color has-text-color has-link-color has-liquid-small-font-size\" style=\"padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--liquid-large);line-height:1.2\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"10px\"}}}} -->\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.5\">Je suis moi-même l'heureuse propriétaire d’un chien et j’ai connu cette seconde de panique, celle où mon poilu ne répond plus, où je l’appelles et rien ne bouge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"5px\"}}}} -->\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.5\">Cette sensation froide dans le ventre, des nuits et jours passées à chercher les chiens de mes amis qui pour certains n'ont jamais été retrouvés. Je ne l’oublie pas.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"5px\"}}}} -->\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.5\">C’est exactement là qu’est né Naturap’Pets.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"5px\"}}}} -->\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.5\">J’ai voulu un univers où la sécurité est maître et simple.Où l’on équipe son animal avec confiance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"5px\"}}}} -->\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.5\">Où chaque produit est pensé pour faciliter la vie, pas pour la compliquer.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"5px\"}}}} -->\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.5\">Mon poilu m’a inspiré..</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"5px\"}}}} -->\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.5\">Disons qu’ici, le vrai patron est à quatre pattes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"right\",\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"lineHeight\":\"1.5\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"5px\"}}},\"textColor\":\"custom-bleu-1\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-right has-custom-bleu-1-color has-text-color\" style=\"margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.5\"><em>Célia - Fondatrice de Natura'Pets</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->",
  "syncStatus": "unsynced"
}